Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.89,0:00:06.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind. Open your mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.77,0:00:22.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Far beyond the deep blue Earth,\nyou and I shall meet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.98,0:00:24.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...as a gentle breeze goes by.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.35,0:00:28.35,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.35,0:00:29.82,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.82,0:00:36.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A snow-white feather will come\nfluttering down, swaying gently in the air.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.96,0:00:44.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without holding back, I want to\nenvelope you, my one and only love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.07,0:00:53.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know I have the power to protect\nthe one I love, right here in my hands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.48,0:01:00.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind.\NJust as I've always dreamed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.22,0:01:07.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let the wind carry off\nyour hopes, faraway.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.12,0:01:13.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have wings nobody can see.\NLook, you have them, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.90,0:01:22.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They'll take us to where we can be free.\NAnyone can be free.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.21,0:01:26.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sky is so blue...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.26,0:01:50.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You low-level demons...\nyou're 1,000 years too early!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:53.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.71,0:01:59.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Curses! Where in tarnation can it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.78,0:02:07.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think they'd have\na boss like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.65,0:02:10.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:17.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Aha, I've found it at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.52,0:02:19.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The legendary urn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.46,0:02:23.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Soon I'll be rid of those\nobnoxious goddesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.94,0:02:32.40,AMG episode name,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah! The Devil's Whisper\NComing from an Urn?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:36.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,O Urn of ancient times,\NUrn of Hakushon the Demon King!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.78,0:02:42.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I beg of you, grant my wish!\nI beg of you, open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:48.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to unleash all the\nmisery of the world on them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.53,0:02:52.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Once the Lord of Terror awakens,\nwe demons shall rule the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:56.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have nothing to fear\nfrom those goddesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.94,0:03:02.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's a kitty cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.74,0:03:09.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.38,0:03:10.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.82,0:03:20.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The moment that the\NUrn opens its eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.02,0:03:24.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the bronze-skinned Lord of Terror\nshall be resurrected!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.06,0:03:27.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let the world know misery and despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.47,0:03:31.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.01,0:03:40.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd, would you like some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:41.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.51,0:03:46.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Urd, your favorite show is on now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:47.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.65,0:03:52.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd, I tossed out those weird bottles\nof yours, they were in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.26,0:03:53.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Really....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:54.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.16,0:03:57.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew there was a\nlicensing system for goddesses?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.83,0:04:01.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on, stop sulking,\nit's just a suspension!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:02.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.77,0:04:04.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Skuld!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:06.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a license, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.94,0:04:07.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:12.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,For example, I'm a Goddess 1st Class,\N2nd Category, Unlimited License.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.51,0:04:15.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Class refers to precision\nand power level.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.04,0:04:17.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,''2nd Category'' is a commercial license.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:20.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And ''limited'' indicates\nwhat you're permitted to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:23.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Goddess 2nd Class,\N1st Category, Limited License.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:26.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd's a Goddess 2nd Class,\NAdministration, Limited License.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:31.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And since a license brings with it\nresponsibility as well as privilege...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:34.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...there are penalties for\nthose who neglect their duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:39.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you can get your license\nsuspended just like that, if you lie all the\ntime!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.37,0:04:42.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault...I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.77,0:04:46.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. A penalty's a penalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.11,0:04:50.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, that's right!\NLearn your lesson once in a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:54.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Suspension, huh?\nI'd better watch out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:58.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you guys, all this talk\nI've been hearing from you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:05:00.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out! She's going to explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:04.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is all just a joke to you, isn't it?\NSummoning...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:07.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.93,0:05:09.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:13.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If she uses her powers during her\nsuspension, they'll revoke her license.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.34,0:05:16.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So she does know that's the deal, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:19.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, I'm going to\nquit being a goddess!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.78,0:05:21.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:24.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we were too hard on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.08,0:05:29.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing Urd, I'm sure having her powers\ntaken away must be stressing her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:32.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So how long are they\nsuspending her license?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.42,0:05:33.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,For this long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:35.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Five months?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:39.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Five days? Five minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:40.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me Five years?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.93,0:05:43.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fifty years in Earth terms...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:45.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fifty years?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:51.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there some kind of course she can\ntake to get her license back sooner?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:53.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, actually, there is, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:54.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.71,0:05:58.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's a seminar in Heaven,\nlasting thirty years...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.05,0:05:59.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.02,0:06:01.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way she can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:05.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Really, who knew that\nwalking was such a drag?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.89,0:06:09.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?\NYou don't look too happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:12.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, I have a lot going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.36,0:06:15.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, would you mind\nlending me that bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.13,0:06:17.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind, but you've got one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:18.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:23.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you don't know that you\ncan't ride a motorcycle without a license.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.14,0:06:25.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,License, license, license!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:27.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Another license?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:30.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd? Hey, wait! Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.38,0:06:32.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down! Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.65,0:06:34.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Consideration for others,\nfor other cars and for this town{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:37.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So they'll give me a license here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.92,0:06:40.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it should be a cinch\nto get one for a moped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.39,0:06:42.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All righty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:45.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They said it costs money!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:47.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What did you expect?{\i0}\NThey said it costs money!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.45,0:06:48.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Lend me some!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:51.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's something I can't help you with!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.37,0:06:55.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, darn! All right, then! I'll get\na part-time job, I'll do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:57.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your eyes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.07,0:06:58.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What? Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.14,0:07:05.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that scared me.\nI thought she'd found us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:06.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Inoue Pharmacy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:08.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Inoue Pharmacy{\i0}\nIf there ever was a perfect job for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:11.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...this has to be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.52,0:07:14.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They said I have to have\na pharmacist's license.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:16.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:18.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hair salon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.39,0:07:21.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Blowfish Restaurant\NFugukichi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:29.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I have an errand to run,\nso I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:32.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta study for my license...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.71,0:07:35.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you know\nyou could get suspended if...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:37.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,License? Suspended?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.98,0:07:42.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I sense you people are ready\nfor a change, so please vote for me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:43.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,License...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:47.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Car in front! Stop, or\nyour license will be suspended!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.89,0:07:52.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,For crying out loud! License, license\nsuspension, that's all I ever hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:56.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In that case, embrace my powers...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:58.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:07:59.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:05.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you smushed my castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.41,0:08:07.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.79,0:08:22.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! That's amazing!\NAre you a magician, Big Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:26.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:31.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just one more push!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.10,0:08:38.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening and welcome!\NOh, it's you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:40.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.34,0:08:41.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.63,0:08:44.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That was your power just now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.45,0:08:45.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.95,0:08:48.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:50.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need a license here, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:53.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to live as a\nhuman being from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.99,0:08:55.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:09:00.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Will that be all?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.40,0:09:03.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The dessert special and\na pineapple milk float.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.93,0:09:06.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And the sweet red bean soup\nand a mountain crepe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.87,0:09:09.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um, let me repeat your order.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.27,0:09:14.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,One seafood macaroni gratin and\none salmon and scallop spaghetti...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.08,0:09:16.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and a clam soup and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:19.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Lady, when are you gonna take my\norder?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:20.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I need an ashtray!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.85,0:09:23.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be with you in a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:26.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she's gonna be okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:29.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I just hope she doesn't\npush herself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:31.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.39,0:09:35.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, girlie. What are you\ngonna do about my clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.40,0:09:40.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't just stand there,\nyou gotta speak up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:42.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:43.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:45.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:48.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, didn't catch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.01,0:09:49.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd, don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.80,0:09:53.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up...that's what I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:10:00.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The hell with licenses!\NThe hell with my suspension!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:03.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm through with being\na goddess or a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.09,0:10:06.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What difference does it make,\nI'm useless and nobody needs me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.93,0:10:10.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then assume your true form now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.20,0:10:12.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unleash your demonic powers!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:14.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:17.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You are the Lord of Terror's\nrightful heir...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.81,0:10:21.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm Urd, Goddess 2nd Class,\NAdministrative Category, Limited\NLicense...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:25.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, even if you're unable to\nuse your powers?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.11,0:10:26.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:29.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Accept me now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.05,0:10:32.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and you'll have unlimited use of a\ngreater power than you've ever known!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.96,0:10:33.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:37.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It must be tedious to have to submit\nto all these restrictions as a goddess.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.93,0:10:41.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing suits you more\nthan the freedom of a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.06,0:10:45.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Act now, and I'll throw in a\nspecial servant, just for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:48.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Demon, did you say?\NDon't give me that nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.30,0:10:51.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have such hatred for\ndemons?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.14,0:10:53.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When the purest demonic blood\nruns in your veins!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.98,0:10:55.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's...that's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.31,0:11:00.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It goes against nature, for a Black-\NWinged\nbeing to be on the goddesses' side.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:02.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Think it over carefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:06.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're not going to force you to do\nanything, you shall only do as you wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.69,0:11:08.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.19,0:11:11.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, take a good look at yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.43,0:11:16.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now release the demonic power in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:20.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.14,0:11:24.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.63,0:11:28.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've forgotten that name...\nwhat I used to be called!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.48,0:11:31.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But no! How can that be, Urd?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.65,0:11:37.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My name is the Lord of Terror!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:38.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:41.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All of you people...know my true name!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:44.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I shall destroy everything in my path!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.03,0:11:46.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:48.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.41,0:12:01.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:05.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe Urd really turned\nout to be the Lord of Terror...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.11,0:12:07.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Lord of Terror?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.44,0:12:08.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.44,0:12:12.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The day before I received my\ncommission as a 1st Class Goddess...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.49,0:12:16.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Belldandy, there is something\nI must tell you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.89,0:12:17.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.89,0:12:23.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A legend among goddesses and\ndemons...\nyou know of the Lord of Terror, do you\nnot?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:24.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.33,0:12:29.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When this Lord descends, the earth\nshall rupture, its axis shall be twisted...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:33.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...there will be confusion among\nthe people, and after 7 days of fire...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:35.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...all shall be destroyed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:36.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.45,0:12:41.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Urd...might very well be\nthe Lord of Terror's heir.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:42.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.08,0:12:46.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have sealed her demonic blood, so\nI don't believe it will ever be unleashed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:50.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But should the demons ever make\na serious attempt to lure her...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:52.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...to their side,\nit might not be failsafe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:58.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If that side of her should ever manifest,\nyou must notify me immediately.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:12:59.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:04.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So Urd isn't really your older sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.41,0:13:10.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd and I were born to different mothers,\nyou see, and Urd's mother is actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.38,0:13:12.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A demon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:17.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even so...Urd is still\nour precious big sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:21.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Our beloved big sister,\nwho shares half of our bloodline.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.62,0:13:24.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Of course she is...but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:28.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...wouldn't the Almighty One do\nsomething about it, in that case?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.26,0:13:33.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He will send goddesses under his direct\ncommand, from the Combat Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:35.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Combat Division?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.77,0:13:40.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. These goddesses are called\NValkyries, and their duty is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.18,0:13:44.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...to completely annihilate\nthe source of all evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:47.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Isn't there something we can\ndo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.45,0:13:51.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember when\NMarller was here before?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.55,0:13:53.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.02,0:13:58.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A catalyst is necessary for a\ndemon to appear here on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.16,0:13:59.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That means that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:02.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You mean there must\nbe a CD or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:03.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:08.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Either we destroy it, or use its\ncounterpart to seal the demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.39,0:14:09.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.83,0:14:13.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,However, once I've sealed her...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.38,0:14:18.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...Urd will be forced to wander\nin solitude until the end of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:19.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.81,0:14:23.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's no good...\nwhat are we supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:25.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.66,0:14:29.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What in blue blazes happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:33.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So you've come at last.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:36.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd? What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:41.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, so it's you...the servant\nI was promised as a bonus.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:46.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You have no right to call me a servant,\nwith that weird outfit on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.68,0:14:49.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The way you're dressed\nisn't much different!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.25,0:14:52.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You shut up!\NDon't compare me with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.35,0:14:58.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!\NHow can Urd be this powerful?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.82,0:15:03.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Behold, I am the\NLord of Terror's rightful heir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.73,0:15:07.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Know how powerful I am!\nI shall destroy everything in my path!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.79,0:15:12.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Lord of Terror? Ridiculous!\NHow can a goddess like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:16.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Humph! I've quit being a goddess,\nit was too stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.91,0:15:20.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have discovered my true power!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:23.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Preposterous...how could Urd be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.78,0:15:26.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But come to think of it,\nthe legend did say...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:29.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the Lord of Terror would be\nbronze-skinned.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:32.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she always did have\na demonic personality!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:34.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you muttering about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:36.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My lord!{\i0}\NWhat are you muttering about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:39.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you doubt me, would you like\nto experience my power firsthand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:42.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly not, my lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.80,0:15:48.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get her to join with me, and\nmake those wretched goddesses suffer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.37,0:15:53.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,With the power I have at my disposal,\nmere goddesses will be no match for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.94,0:15:56.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What...Yes, my lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:16:01.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Along with those annoying goddesses,\nwe're going to destroy this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:06.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If I may be so bold...\nI have a strategy in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.26,0:16:07.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:11.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is getting interesting!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.89,0:16:15.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So you're not going to\nnotify the Almighty One?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.40,0:16:20.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No. If Urd has truly awakened as the\NLord of Terror, the Almighty One will\nshow...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:23.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...no mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:25.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.64,0:16:29.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get Urd to change her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:30.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:34.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Taking the burden on by yourself?\NYou can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:35.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Skuld...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:39.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she's become the Lord of Terror,\nnothing can change...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.09,0:16:42.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the fact that Urd is my big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:44.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you, Big Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.39,0:16:47.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's strike Urd down together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:48.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:49.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What good will striking her down do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.93,0:16:51.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oops...{\i0}\NWhat good will striking her down do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:54.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, if Urd hasn't\nlost her whole soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:58.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I don't see her doing\nany major damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:16:59.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:03.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But the problem is...\naccording to the legend...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:08.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the Lord of Terror possesses\nthe Ultimate Destruction Program.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.08,0:17:09.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimate Destruction?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:11.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Program?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.36,0:17:22.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But Big Sister! If it's a program, then\nthere's got to be a vaccine or\nsomething...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.17,0:17:25.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:32.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Banpei!{\i0}\NWhat is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:37.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! That's it!\NBehold my overwhelming power!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.83,0:17:42.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,First off, I'm going to smash your\ngoddess headquarters into oblivion!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:44.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.72,0:17:46.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.69,0:17:52.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:56.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what you wanted to do\nwith your powers, Urd?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:18:02.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're the one who always looks\nout for us. You'd never want to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:05.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Show us how strong your soul is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.57,0:18:07.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:12.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy! Skuld!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.05,0:18:14.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't pay any attention to them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:17.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're the ones who\ntook away your powers!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:18.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.42,0:18:21.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's their fault that you got\nyour license suspended!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.75,0:18:23.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Suspended...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.93,0:18:26.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.36,0:18:28.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right! Demonic power...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:30.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.87,0:18:35.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you call an attack\nagainst the Lord of Terror?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.74,0:18:38.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What the...there's no effect at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.24,0:18:44.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't have you\nunderestimating my power, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.25,0:18:48.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Banpei! Deploy the\NMagnetic Net Wire Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:49.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.99,0:18:57.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.50,0:19:01.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Skuld!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.10,0:19:05.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Banpei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.10,0:19:08.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good! She's too powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.47,0:19:13.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is this supposed to hurt me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.78,0:19:20.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.35,0:19:24.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is my Powered Exoskeleton,\NHercules 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.25,0:19:27.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this sounds kind of familiar...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.32,0:19:30.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I used the engine\nfrom your bike as a power source.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.66,0:19:33.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:35.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You fools...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.59,0:19:40.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Give it all you've got, Beemer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.09,0:19:44.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, I guess 45 horsepower\nwasn't enough after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.84,0:19:46.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You should have realized that sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.61,0:19:48.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keiichi!{\i0}\NYou should have realized that sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:52.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ooooh...that tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:57.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! The vibrations\nare loosening the bolts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:19:58.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bolts?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:20:01.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:06.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to remove all the bolts!\NNot just mine, but all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:07.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.83,0:20:12.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Turn...fly...\nrelease yourself from your bonds...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:15.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I command you all to descend to earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:18.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.15,0:20:26.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.82,0:20:28.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:30.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.42,0:20:33.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You used up your powers,\njust as I anticipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:36.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is the moment\nI've been waiting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:39.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So Urd and the giant robot\nwere just decoys?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.53,0:20:44.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't have her doing you know\nwhat.\NThose were the Lord of Terror's\ninstructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.60,0:20:48.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'm going to seal you up now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.94,0:20:51.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.38,0:20:54.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.18,0:21:00.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.01,0:21:03.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...did you have to get in the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.82,0:21:06.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.38,0:21:09.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Curses! I've got to seal her\nbefore she wakes up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.99,0:21:11.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.89,0:21:16.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, Belldandy's come to!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:21.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice but to try again later.\nI can probably think of some use for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.81,0:21:26.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Marller, what are you\ngoing to do with Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.78,0:21:30.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows? You know what they say...\nonly the devil knows!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:32.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.65,0:21:35.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? What happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:38.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi's been captured by Marller.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.42,0:21:39.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.79,0:21:44.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When Marller was about to seal you\naway,\nhe jumped in to protect you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.93,0:21:46.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's when she...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.13,0:21:49.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So Keiichi was taken in my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.67,0:21:50.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.90,0:21:55.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not only has Urd turned into the Lord of\NTerror, but if she's in league with Marller...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.94,0:21:58.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...there's going to be trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.11,0:22:00.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm removing my power limiter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.64,0:22:01.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.74,0:22:05.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Removing your power limiter\nis a huge offense!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.31,0:22:09.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm going to stop Urd...\nand if I'm going to save Keiichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.58,0:22:11.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm going to need my full power.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.95,0:22:13.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.42,0:22:17.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have to...I have to if\nI'm going to save Keiichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.23,0:22:24.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Almighty One...just this once,\nplease forgive my willfulness...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.47,0:22:30.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Always believe in yourself and your\NDreams.\NYou have a wing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.61,0:22:35.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I love you so much it hurts...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.61,0:22:41.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And it hurts me that\nI can't tell you how I feel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.28,0:22:46.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You and I have matching hearts...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.32,0:22:51.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So we must share the\nsame scars deep down inside.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.46,0:22:56.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But now that I'm in your arms,\nI think I can catch...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.90,0:23:01.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...your pounding heartbeat this time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:07.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nobody else matters...\NAll we have to do is gaze at each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.38,0:23:12.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all right for your heart to flutter...\NAll we have to do is love each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.78,0:23:17.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your heart, and\nride that favorable wind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.78,0:23:23.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't run away from happiness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.93,0:23:28.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll always be waiting for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.83,0:23:34.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So come rest your wings anytime.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.04,0:23:39.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all right to cry...\nanytime you need to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.04,0:23:44.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just want to see you again...\NAll we have to do is love each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.68,0:23:49.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your heart, and\nride that favorable wind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.65,0:23:55.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just want you to be happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.46,0:23:59.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Lord of Terror's fury\nis about to be unleashed!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.19,0:24:03.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Possessed by demons, the goddess\nunleashes the forbidden power.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.50,0:24:06.97,AMG episode name,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Ah! The Savior of the\NWorld\NArrives with the Sound of the Flute?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.97,0:24:10.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,First a battle with a robot...\nand now monsters?
